import React from 'react'
import { Flex, Text, Button, HStack, Box, Center } from '@chakra-ui/core'
import { MdBookmarkBorder, MdControlPoint } from 'react-icons/md'
import {BsClipboardData} from 'react-icons/bs'

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Box width={["100%", "100%", "100%", "90%"]}>
      <Flex justifyContent="space-between" px="10" py="2">
        <Flex>
          <Center>
          <Text>探索</Text>
          <Text>题库</Text>
          <Text>讨论</Text>
          <Text>竞赛</Text>
          <Text>企业</Text>
          </Center>
        </Flex>
        <HStack>
          <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdBookmarkBorder />} colorScheme="teal" variant="outline">下载App</Button>
          <Button size="sm" leftIcon={<MdControlPoint />} colorScheme="yellow" variant="outline">Plus会员</Button>
          <BsClipboardData />
        </HStack>
      </Flex>        
    </Box>
  )
}
